column2: [1] Some values are zero due to rounding.

Note: The estimates are based on the 2010 Census and reflect changes to the April 1, 2010 population due to the Count Question Resolution program and geographic program revisions. All geographic boundaries for the 2014 population estimates series except statistical area delineations are as of January 1, 2014. The Office of Management and Budget's statistical area delineations for metropolitan, micropolitan, and combined statistical areas, as well as metropolitan divisions, are those issued by that agency in February 2013 http://www.whitehouse.gov/sites/default/files/omb/bulletins/2013/b13-01.pdf. For population estimates methodology statements, see http://www.census.gov/popest/methodology/index.html.
